--- ## Benchmark Methodology The assessment uses progressive load testing to determine sustainable
throughput for each platform component. Tests measure: - **Throughput capacity** — maximum
sustainable requests per second - **Response latency** — median, 95th, and 99th percentile response
times - **Resource utilization** — CPU and memory consumption under load - **Stability** — error
rates, connection reliability, and recovery behavior All tests were conducted against the live
deployment with representative workloads. --- ## Agent Conversation Performance | Service |
